   3.9119029150224075`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"25a6b9db-ed04-4281-9d33-\
49d0a6a45336"],

Cell["\<\
The disjoint  diagrams at third order are 5760 in total. These are \
distributed as follows:
i) 576 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the antidiagonal;
ii) 576 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in the diagonal;
iii) 768 Bogoliubov diagrams dressed in both the diagonal and the antidiagonal;
iv) 576 Direct diagrams dressed in the left propagator;
v) 576 Direct diagrams dressed in the right propagator;
vi) 768 Direct diagrams dressed in both the left and the right propagator;
vii) 576 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator above;
viii) 576 Exchange diagrams dressed in the propagator below;
ix) 768 Exchange diagrams dressed in both the above and below propagator;\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8746447846491413`*^9, 3.874644822571206*^9}, {
   3.874644938314557*^9, 3.874644942272763*^9}, {3.8836802941172266`*^9, 
